No. 10-6508. Larry Arnold Young, Petitioner v. Patricia R. Stansberry, Warden. 562 U.S. 979, 131 S. Ct. 435,

178 L. Ed. 2d 319,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8199. October 18, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certio-rari dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 372 Fed. Appx. 394.
